==English==

===Verb===
{{en-verb|shred|shreds|shredded|shredding}}
# To partition into narrow pieces or strips.
# {{snowboarding}}: To ride agressively.
# {{bodybuilding}}: To drop fat and water weight before a competition.

===Noun===
'''shred'''  (''plural:'' '''[[shreds]]''')
# A long, narrow piece cut or torn off; a strip.
# In general, a fragment; a piece; a particle.
# ''McDonald's lingo'' shredded [[lettuce]].

